.SH NAME
.PP
tollgate-ssl-apply - Apply an SSL certificate


.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\fBtollgate ssl apply [ [key-file]] [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Apply an SSL certificate for HTTPS access.

.PP
Without arguments, generates a self-signed certificate for the router's hostname.
With a single PEM file, splits combined cert+key.
With two files, uses separate cert and key files.


.SH OPTIONS
.PP
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for apply

.PP
\fB-y\fP, \fB--yes\fP[=false]
	Skip confirmation prompt


